data.description: Beautiful well maintained home is simply gorgeous, it has all the bells and whistles for a home of this size. This 3bedroom 2 full bathroom home is conveniently  located in the heart of most sought out city of Lynn Haven.Inside features luxury laminated floors throughout home Kitchen has stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, as you walk though the home there's beautiful chandeliers ceiling fans and bright lights... Outside of Home has ,Gerald roof ( which is metal)  solar panels (seller will payoff at closing) and a patio with total privacy due to the entire property being fenced in,  the outside space is great for entertaining your family and friends . Excellent curb appeal. This home is a must see!!!Information provided is deemed reliable but is not guaranteed and should be independently verify by the buyer.
